403
00:38:15,119 --> 00:38:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] u tišini s Bogom i onako baš pitamo sami sebe kako sam ja.

404
00:38:20,159 --> 00:38:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne ono kao reda radi.

405
00:38:21,719 --> 00:38:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je moje tijelo, noga, stopalo, glava, to radimo na tebi.

406
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:26,679
[SPEAKER_01] Kako sam ja uopće sada?

407
00:38:26,679 --> 00:38:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] To mi zaboravimo i samo maknemo sa strane.

408
00:38:29,119 --> 00:38:31,280
[SPEAKER_01] Što ja sad osjećam?

409
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:34,139
[SPEAKER_01] I onda krenu, kad ostaneš u toj tišini, u sabranosti,

410
00:38:34,139 --> 00:38:37,960
