478
00:42:07,699 --> 00:42:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo imati vrijeme kad stanemo.

479
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,039
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo imati vrijeme kad stanemo same sa sobom,

480
