496
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja bi došla u šutnje.

497
00:42:44,340 --> 00:42:46,320
[SPEAKER_01] Čim uđem na rata od šutnje, evo ga.

498
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ja plaćem, ja znam da ja to trebam odraditi.

499
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ja trebam plakat, ja se trebam izotugovati.

500
00:42:50,739 --> 00:42:52,199
