518
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] To je još jedna stvar koju moraš.

519
00:43:32,019 --> 00:43:33,239
[SPEAKER_01] Poćeš napraviti čevku u knjižici.

520
00:43:33,239 --> 00:43:33,840
[SPEAKER_01] To nije to.

521
00:43:33,840 --> 00:43:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] Challenge.

522
00:43:34,739 --> 00:43:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] Challenge.

523
00:43:35,380 --> 00:43:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da dozvoljavamo sebi da budemo ljubljene.

524
00:43:37,539 --> 00:43:38,780
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo da se radi u tijelovježbi.

525
00:43:38,780 --> 00:43:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo da se radi u formaciji.

526
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:41,860
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje.

527
00:43:41,860 --> 00:43:43,559
